# Claudia never ships or syncs a person's data.
# The person's memory, transcripts, and deliverables live under ~/.claudia/ on
# their own machine — never in this repo. This entry is a belt-and-braces guard
# in case anyone ever creates a local .claudia/ inside the project tree.
.claudia/
**/.claudia/

# Scratch / local
.DS_Store
node_modules/
*.log
.env
.env.*
